rows.label: qst002205_msg0001
rows.name:
You're looking for info on that
Choir girl Mellica?

rows.label: qst002205_msg0002
rows.name:
Mmmm... Sorry, but I don't really
know a lot about her.

rows.label: qst002205_msg0003
rows.name:
Maybe you should try asking that
Invidian girl, Albina.

rows.label: qst002205_msg0004
rows.name:
She's a refugee, and she kept saying
she was going to make it into the Choir
no matter what.

rows.label: qst002205_msg0005
rows.name:
But I haven't seen her around lately.
Not sure what she's up to.

rows.label: qst002205_msg0006
rows.name: That's about all I know, I'm afraid.
